Unsurprisingly the taste is very close to the original [[Full_Throttle]] with
less citrus, more notes of fruit. Like cranberry. It no longer reminds me as
strongly of sour gummy worms as the original does; much duller flavor; it is a
mild taste but, although the can promises this, it doesn't particularly taste
like blue agave.

